These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-1::.
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, dog, turtle
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, soccer
1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the right of the owner of the dog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| Pet     | chinchilla | dog    | turtle   |
| Sport   | badminton  | soccer | baseball |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, juice
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, satire, scientific
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5
2. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person watching satire movies##5
3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
4. the person watching family movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching scientific movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |       3       |
| Beverage      | cola   | juice  | hot-chocolate |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | family | scientific    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-3::.
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, nigerian, russian
3 different pets are kept: hamster, mouse, rat
1. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rat##5
2. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rat##5
3. the chinese is somewhere to the right of the nigerian##5
4. the russian is on the left of the chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |
| Nationality   | nigerian | russian | chinese |
| Pet           | mouse    | rat     | hamster |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-4::.
There 3 different types of food: corn, plum, tomato
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, golf, soccer
1. the person eating corn is somewhere to the left of the person eating plum##5
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is in the middle##1
3. the person eating plum is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##5
4. the person eating corn is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is golf##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Food    | tomato | corn     | plum   |
| Sport   | golf   | biathlon | soccer |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-5::.
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, spanish, turkish
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, scooter, trike
1. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the trike is the egyptian##1
3. the turkish is somewhere to the right of the egyptian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Nationality   | spanish | egyptian | turkish   |
| Transport     | scooter | trike    | quad-bike |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: dancing, gardening, rock-climbing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, metal, techno
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the fan of techno##1
2. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##5
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Hobby         | gardening | dancing | rock-climbing |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep   | metal   | techno        |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-7::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  security-guard, software-developer, teacher
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, skiing, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##5
2. the security-guard is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
3. the software-developer is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1        |     2      |         3          |
| Job     | security-guard | teacher    | software-developer |
| Sport   | badminton      | volleyball | skiing             |

