.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-8::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, drawing, reading
The people have 3 different jobs:  designer, fisherman, pilot
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the fisherman##1
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
3. the designer is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
4. the designer is somewhere to the left of the fisherman##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Hobby   | reading | drawing  | baking    |
| Job     | pilot   | designer | fisherman |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-9::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, lemonade
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, quad-bike, scooter
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
2. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##5
3. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person driving the scooter is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |    3     |
| Beverage    | 7up       | coffee   | lemonade |
| Transport   | quad-bike | airplane | scooter  |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-10::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  engineer, freelancer, mechanic
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, reggae, salsa
1. the mechanic is on the far left or far right##3
2. the fan of salsa is somewhere to the right of the fan of house##5
3. the fan of house is between the fan of salsa and the fan of reggae##2
4. the freelancer is on the left of the mechanic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |    3     |
| Job           | engineer | freelancer | mechanic |
| Music-Genre   | reggae   | house      | salsa    |

