There are 3 different nationalities: australian, chinese, indian
1. the chinese is on the right of the indian##1
2. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking fanta##5
3. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Beverage      | milk   | 7up     | fanta      |
| Nationality   | indian | chinese | australian |

