.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-12::.
There 3 different types of food: cabbage, cauliflower, lettuce
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, subway, train
1. the person eating cabbage is somewhere to the left of the person driving the train##5
2. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the left of the person eating lettuce##5
3. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the right of the person eating cabbage##5
4. the person driving the subway is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |    3    |
| Food        | cabbage | cauliflower | lettuce |
| Transport   | subway  | bus         | train   |

