.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-14::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea, water
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, adventure, documentary
1. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
2. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
3. the person drinking water is the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |   2    |      3      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | water  | tea         |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure     | action | documentary |

