.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-20::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, country, d&b
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, tram, van
1. the fan of blues is in the middle##1
2. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the left of the person driving the tram##5
3. the person driving the van is on the left of the fan of d&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2   |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | country | blues | d&b  |
| Transport     | scooter | van   | tram |

